title: The Happening TS VCD Kamera & Bald Audio(non standard VCD)
description:
This is KAMERAS Source through a few filters and an 18 hr MPG encode and is as clear as the AVI 

VIDEO 480x384 VBR 25Fps PAL 16:9

AUDIO 128Kbps CBR Stereo

This is a non standard VCD @480x384 to give higher quality playback on tv will play fine on most DVD Players

This is better than the BALD release in my opinion it certainly gives a better encode to MPG but has subtitles..

SAMPLE INCLUDED (sample is a re encode of the MPG as my editor wouldnt split variable bitrate for some reason)?
